$(document).ready(function(){$(".editable").editable({type:"text",name:"username",url:"/post",title:"Edit username",});$("#status").editable({prepend:"not selected",source:[{value:1,text:"Activated"},{value:2,text:"Pending"},{value:3,text:"Deleted"}],display:function(d,c){var a={1:"text-success",2:"text-warning",3:"text-danger"},b=$.grep(c,function(e){return e.value==d});if(b.length){$(this).text(b[0].text).removeClass("text-success text-warning text-danger");$(this).text(b[0].text).addClass(a[d])}}});$.mockjax({url:"/post",responseTime:200})});